testocr.png: Cedric himself knew nothing whatever about it. It had never been even mentionde to him. He knew that his papa had been an Englishman, because his mamma had told him so; but then hs papa had died when he was so little a boy that he could not remember very much about him, except that he was big, and had blue eyes and a long mustache, and that it was a splendid thung to be carried around the room on his shoulder.
